        "When you shop at a department store or large clothing retailer, you’ll often see any tailored jacket for sale listed as a “blazer.” But not every jacket with lapels and buttons can accurately bear this name! To understand the differences between blazers, suit jackets, and sport coats, we must delve into each type of garment’s […]",
