        "The Old Money aesthetic is not about having a closet overflowing with clothes but a curated collection of high-quality garments that can be mixed and matched to create many looks. This is the concept of a capsule wardrobe – a minimal yet comprehensive selection of clothing, footwear, and accessories that serves as the foundation for any personal style. A […]",
